  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1; \u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in price of pot; Decision today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Increase the price of an Irathal pan to Rs 300 or not? All Sri Lanka Bakery Owners Association said that it will be decided today.",
        "Its chairman NK Jayawardena said that a special discussion will be held with the Commerce Minister this morning.",
        "He also mentioned that there will be a discussion about wheat flour shortage and other issues faced by the bakery owners.",
        "NK Jayawardena, President of the All Sri Lankan Bakery Owners Association has indicated that the demand for their products has already decreased by 50 percent due to the increase in the price of bakery products including pan.",
        "Accordingly, if the prices of bakery products are increased further, the industry will collapse, he added.",
        "It is noteworthy that the All Sri Lankan Bakery Owners Association announced last Saturday that due to the shortage of wheat flour in the market and the increase in the price of wheat flour, the price of one Irathal pan has to be increased to 300 rupees."
      ],
